e, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "thefederalist.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASGJ067F8.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://thefederalist.com/2026/03/17/you-cant-have-a-free-country-when-the-government-makes-choices-for-you/", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "You Can\u2019t Have A Free Country When The Government Makes Choices For You. Americans have an incredible array of choices for food and consumer goods, but government monopolies in education, health care, and energy are ruining our lives. ", "last_comment_created": 1773879277911, "content": "", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 12, "score_up": 511, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "Americans have an array of choices for food and goods, but government monopolies in education, health care, and energy are ruining our lives.", "large_image": "eCRJBzxH4S6AxHvF.png", "title": "You Can't Have A Free Country When Govt Makes Choices For You"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASGJ1EVhG", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 93, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8497256, "raw_content": "We got 30+\" of snow this weekend.  Roads are still shit.  Plow goes through and pushes about two feet of snow into the intersection.  An SUV  turns right and is instantly stuck.  I pull up and get out to give him a push.  He's not in that bad.  I tell him to turn his wheels straight........he turns them left.  I tell him to back up, he goes forward.  I tell him to go forward he turns his wheels to the right.  I'm like how fucking stupid are you?\n\nI tell him to start rocking back and forth, he guns it.  Finally I resort to hand signals to which he still fucking doesn't get.  Fucking clown buries me in slop but I finally get him out.  The entire time he never speaks a word.  \n\nI get back in my truck and just drive off shaking my head.  Now I admit I can be a little retarded but suddenly it hit me after he was almost out.  The fucker was probably an illegal that didn't speak a lick of English.  I looked down on my slop filled pants and just said FUUUUCK.  A 30 second job took ten minutes because the fucker did the opposite of everything I told him to do.  I never even really looked at the guy until he was almost unstuck.  You just help people when you can.  But these fucking clowns need to go back.  They are a hazard in every way.  ", "author": "4444444444444", "created": 1773865188732, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "IBentMyWookie", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "So I pull up to a guy stuck in the snowbank.", "last_comment_created": 1773878975509, "content": "<p>We got 30+&quot; of snow this weekend.  Roads are still shit.  Plow goes through and pushes about two feet of snow into the intersection.  An SUV  turns right and is instantly stuck.  I pull up and get out to give him a push.  He's not in that bad.  I tell him to turn his wheels straight........he turns them left.  I tell him to back up, he goes forward.  I tell him to go forward he turns his wheels to the right.  I'm like how fucking stupid are you?</p>\n<p>I tell him to start rocking back and forth, he guns it.  Finally I resort to hand signals to which he still fucking doesn't get.  Fucking clown buries me in slop but I finally get him out.  The entire time he never speaks a word.</p>\n<p>I get back in my truck and just drive off shaking my head.  Now I admit I can be a little retarded but suddenly it hit me after he was almost out.  The fucker was probably an illegal that didn't speak a lick of English.  I looked down on my slop filled pants and just said FUUUUCK.  A 30 second job took ten minutes because the fucker did the opposite of everything I told him to do.  I never even really looked at the guy until he was almost unstuck.  You just help people when you can.  But these fucking clowns need to go back.  They are a hazard in every way.</p>\n", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 11, "score_up": 94, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2034103558463778980", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASGJ06OUS", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 355, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "kek", "id": 8496390, "raw_content": "", "author": "DCSucks", "created": 1773839154848, "profile_picture": "HROqPiS20z4h", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DepartmentOfOffense", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASGJ06OUS.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/Channel6ixNEWS/status/2034103558463778980?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\"I am Indian Saar we need 10,000 more H1Bs Saar\" \ud83d\ude02\ud83d\ude02\ud83d\ude02\ud83d\ude02", "last_comment_created": 1773873168344, "content": "", "score_down": 3, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_